title: Viktor Myagkov
text:
Viktor Alekseyevich Myagkov (; born 2 February 1985) is a former <a href="Russia">Russia</a>n professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a>er.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Premier%20League">Russian Premier League</a> in 2005 for <a href="FC%20Shinnik%20Yaroslavl">FC Shinnik Yaroslavl</a>.
